definitions.definition: A member of a Native American tribe originally inhabiting Onondaga County , New York .

main_definition: A member of a Native American tribe originally inhabiting Onondaga County , New York .

definitions.definition: The language of the Onondaga people.
An ancient village of the Onondaga people in what is now in upstate New York that served as the capital of the Iroquois Confederacy.
A town in Onondaga County , New York , United States .
